{"tid":2019221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15萬人染疫 土國律師告中國隱瞞","createTime":"2020-05-16T06:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T06:36:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8a80bc9c3f94c3842adce757a25d0184614ac301","tid":2019221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200516/LXHHURPJ3SY4CDJJUUISYQPJ64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200516%2FLXHHURPJ3SY4CDJJUUISYQPJ64%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=e2f934e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200516%2FLXHHURPJ3SY4CDJJUUISYQPJ64%2F&h=77cfcad1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200516/LXHHURPJ3SY4CDJJUUISYQPJ64/</a><br />\n<br />\n15萬人染疫 土國律師告中國隱瞞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589559136_0e70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589559136_0e70.jpg&h=e2cf5007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土耳其伊斯坦堡的墳場有指定部份專埋葬武漢肺炎死者。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n土耳其近15萬人感染武漢肺炎，逾4,000人病栍。當地兩名律師指控中國瞞報武漢肺炎疫情及病毒可傳人，令很多公司蒙受損失，並向安卡拉民事初審法院提起訴訟，向中國索償。<br />\n<br />\n指不少企業蒙受損失<br />\n<br />\n兩名律師。。。。。。。並延遲三周才通報病毒傳染性及隱瞞真實病例數字。<br />\n<br />\n梅利赫早前向美聯社透露。。。。。。。。。，「我的客戶相信中國是故意而非疏忽」。<br />\n<br />\n梅利赫又稱，。。。。。。。。，亦可提起訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"}]}